6. Model Estimation Results
This section presents the model results for calculating the probability of a container to be picked up in a specific time slot. The methodology of TOD models was presented in the previous section. Road restrictions imposed by local authorities are also taken into consideration.
The examined terminal operates 24 hours, 7 days per week. For model development, each day was divided into nine different intervals that take into account the restrictions imposed to truck movements (Table 2).
