The typical logit estimation software Biogeme release 2.4 (Bierlaire, 2003 and Bierlaire, 2015) was used for model estimation. The first time interval was used as base interval and the utility in this interval was taken equal to 0.

To better interpret the parameter presented in Table 3 we calculated and plotted the relative

utilities as presented in the Figures 2 and 3. For each parameter the utility was calculated as the

sum of the constant component and the alternative specific coefficient for each parameter, for

example

for

